---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 95
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Cosmic Dream
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=The Round of Existence
---
He who is forgetful of the Self, mistaking the physical body for it, and goes
though innumerable births, is just like one who wanders all over the world in
a dream; and then realizing the Self would only be like the waking up from
the dream-wanderings.
